											<div class="library-item-description">
												<p>
													Non-EU students need to apply for a visa before coming to France. This process can be very long and tiring. You are adviced to start early.
												</p>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<!-- Library item - HOUSING-->
						<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
